items.title: Trump says 'I think we have a deal' on Gaza war
items.description: President Donald Trump said Friday that "I think we have a deal" on ending the Israel-Hamas war, adding, "It's going to be peace."

items.title: Lawmakers push Congress to condemn 'escalation of attacks' on ICE officers after Dallas shooting
items.description: Republicans in Congress introduced a resolution condemning violent attacks on ICE after a deadly shooting at a Dallas facility.

items.title: Comey denies charges, declares 'I am not afraid'
items.description: Former FBI Director James Comey has declared himself "not afraid" of President Trump's Justice Department after he was indicted on federal charges.
